      { path: "/profile_secretary", element: <ProfileSecretary secretaryData={secretaryData} tableData={tableData}/> },
      { path: "/edit_student_profile", element: <EditStudentPage studentData={studentData}/> },
      { path: "/edit_teacher_profile", element: <EditTeacherPage teacherData={teacherData} /> },
      { path: "/edit_secretary_profile", element: <EditSecretaryProfile secretaryData={secretaryData}/> },
      { path: "/", element: <Authentication /> },

      { path: "/create_request", element: <CreateRequest studentData={studentData}/> },
      { path: "/generate_application", element: <GenerateApplicaton studentData={studentData} teacherData={teacherData} requestData={requestData}/> },
